          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", our weekly podcast, is on summer hiatus this week. To tide you over in the meantime, here are some wonderful podcasts recommended by ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
